metadata.name: Queen of Acorns
metadata.description: The particular shape of the luxury chandelier is inspired by the acorn, which is symbolized as decency, luck, power, courage and wealth. The deconstruction style of the small metal leaves brings a sense of modernity to the atmosphere of the home. The chains are Cartier style. The combination of chains and leaves let it shaped like an acorn. The chandelier is available in titanium, gold and rose gold finishing.
